sentences.english: That would be great for JVG. Boost of confidence.
sentences.chinese: 太好了，老範會自信滿滿。

sentences.english: At supper she had two huge plates full of lasagna.
sentences.chinese: 晚飯時她吃了兩大碗滿滿當當的肉醬寬麪條。

sentences.english: The desk was covered with a litter of documents.
sentences.chinese: 書桌上滿滿地放着一堆雜亂的文件。

sentences.english: And the site's cheeky bravado rubs salt in the wounds.
sentences.chinese: 並且網站厚顏無恥並自信滿滿地往它們的傷口上撒鹽。

sentences.english: A large number of my former students showed up, a full room of former students.
sentences.chinese: 結果我以前的那些學生把會議室給撐了個滿滿當當。

sentences.english: I'm the greatest batter in the world! he is full of confidence.
sentences.chinese: “我是世界上最偉大的打擊手，”他自信滿滿。

sentences.english: An overflowing laundry basket stares menacingly from the corner of the room.
sentences.chinese: 房間角落裏，裝得滿滿的洗衣籃不懷好意地盯着我。

sentences.english: Is your tight work schedule forcing you to forego your daily exercises?
sentences.chinese: 你滿滿的工作安排是否迫使你放棄日常鍛鍊？

sentences.english: His bag was heaped with tissues.
sentences.chinese: 他的包中裝了滿滿一包的衛生紙。

sentences.english: Exhibition floors were chock-a-block with racing and sports cars.
sentences.chinese: 上演場地上讓比賽車塞得滿滿的。

sentences.english: Full of cold air around the pain, the eyes of a burning white.
sentences.chinese: 滿滿的冷氣縈繞在周圍，痛的眼前一片灼白。

sentences.english: One table-spoonful to be taken at bed-time.
sentences.chinese: 睡前要喝掉滿滿一湯匙。

sentences.english: I have 4 albums full of stamps.
Full of hope, stand on tiptoe, twinkle star be able to touch.
sentences.chinese: 滿滿的心願，踮起腳，閃爍的許願星就能觸到。

sentences.english: Place a rounded tablespoonful of filling in lower right corner of strip.
sentences.chinese: 舀滿滿一湯匙的餡倒在麪皮的右下角處。
